title: [Weekly-46] 2020.03.15
content:
Weekly visual project - 2020/03/15
The excerpt I’m perfectly happy with all the people who are walking around and just staring at the clouds and looking at the stars and saying, ‘I want to go there.’ But I’m looking at the ground, and I want to fix the pothole that’s right in front of me before I fall in. by Linux Torvalds
